 Jodie Barden , 28 , is mother to eight-year-old Ella and one-year Chloe Chloe , both suffer from Cockayne Syndrome and have a life expectancy of just 12 .
Cockayne disorder is a rare genetic disorder , is characterised by a failure to gain weight , premature ageing , and a small head .
In 2013 , Mrs Barden has made arrangements for both daughters ' funerals .